 their manor? reflected Martin. Can it be that everything has remained the same—those little pears, for example, drying on the veranda roof?)

“Mohicans,” murmured Danilevski pensively.

The room was emptyish. Small divans, a stove with a zigzag pipe, newspapers on wooden holders.

